          playback of podcasts with an intuitive design. In addition, I have
          developed an
          <span class="text-amber-200">E-commerce</span> and dynamic applications
          where I have put into practice my knowledge, optimizing performance and
          accessibility.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl text-pretty border-l-4 border-cyan-600 pl-4"
